OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fbut rather cloudy this evening,
OL,7,Fhowever some late spells of sunshine
OL,8,Fwill develop across southern areas.
OL,9,FOvernight will remain similar with
OL,10,Fsome clear spells, especially across
OL,11,Fthe south. A mild night to come with
OL,12,Flight winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FCloudy in the north with
OL,15,Fbrighter spells in the south. As the
OL,16,Fday goes on, cloud will lift and break
OL,17,Finto the afternoon, leaving a bright
OL,18,Fevening. Feeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
